8\begin{pmatrix} 7 \\ k  \end{pmatrix} = (k+1)\begin{pmatrix} 8 \\ k +1  \end{pmatrix}\,.
n\geq 1
n
8-n=7-(n-1)
 n\binom{8}{n}=n\cdot\frac{8!}{n!(8-n)!}=n\cdot\frac{8\cdot 7!}{n\cdot(n-1)!\cdot(8-n)!}. 
 n\binom{8}{n}=8\cdot\frac{7!}{(n-1)!(8-n)!}. 
 n\binom{8}{n}=8\cdot\frac{7!}{(n-1)!(7-(n-1))!}=8\binom{7}{n-1}. 
